@w2 Long story short: @w2 The Polaris Megacorps lost one of their capital vessels - @w2 the <color=#ffffff>Ilmarinen</color>.
@p9 The vessel was exploring distant systems for the last few years. @w2 Its goal was to find new worlds and new resources. @w2 The company lost contact with the ship about half a year ago. @w2

They have found its trace, @w2 but because of the Zirax patrols getting much more frequent in the months since your people's arrival, @w2 they are not able to officially investigate themselves. @w2 Now they are asking if we could lend them a hand.

