@w2 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> Yes. That's exactly my point! As you might know, my grandpa was the lead engineer on the Hyperion. @w2 He was not lost with the ship only for one simple reason: someone decided to reschedule his shift. @w2 I'm thankful for that, but my grandpa never managed to get rid of the stigma of 'the coward that was left behind'.
@p9 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> My dad moved to Mars with me after my grandpa's sudden death. @w2 I signed up for the fleet right after college, to show what our family is capable of. @w2 My dad said that Grandpa became crazy about this shit. @w2 Pretending the officials just want to silence everyone. @w2 Especially him personally, and the Hyperion Bereaved organization. @w2 All his stories of a 'planned accident.' @w2 The ship 'not being destroyed' and some 'threat' we are facing - all very dramatic.
@p9 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> And, to be honest, until the last 24h, I always thought this old poor man simply could not cope with what happened. @w2 When you showed up on board the Titan, I suddenly remembered one of my grandpa's stories, about some 'black suits' visiting the Hyperion a few days ahead of the mission.
@w2 <color=#9c9c9c>[M]</color> Commander. Please...
@w2 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> I tell you what: 
@p9 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> I've been working on this project for nearly eight years now, and in these last few months, I've looked at this project and I've done the math. @w2 In the last week, and in the last 24 h in particular, so many strange things have happened.@w2 The GRAND and the TITAN each have several squads of marines on board. I checked the manifests yesterday. @w2 We have stashed away tons and tons and tons of high-caliber ammo. @w2 I am an engineer. I know what these formulas and materials are made for. @w2 This is not for asteroid defense. @w2 And now you are coming on board. @w2 And the first thing you do is mess around with the protocols I have been developing for the last five years.
@p9 <color=#9c9c9c>[M]</color> The adjustments we've made are coming directly from Apollon labs. @w2 Dr Greyson and Dr. Dawson?
@w2 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> I know them. @w2 But I have also looked at the changes you made. @w2 These are risky. I am not sure what they should do exactly. @w2 They don't seem to have any function that improves the efficiency of the warp drives.
@w2 <color=#9c9c9c>[M]</color> Rest assured, these have been approved by top specialists- everything is fine.
@w2 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> Rest assured, if something goes wrong .. @w2and someone is harmed .. @w2 and I discover that it was because of your changes .. @w2 nothing will be fine .. @w2 for you.

